      "rdf:value": "<L>2250<pc>10,3<k1>aYc<k2>aYc<h>1<e>1\r\n<hom>1.</hom> <s>aYc</s> ¦ (connected with √ <s>ac</s>, <ab>q.v.</ab>) <ab>cl.</ab> 1. <ab>P.</ab> <ab>Ā.</ab> <s>a/Ycati</s>, <s>˚te</s>, <s>AnaYca</s>, <s>˚ce</s>, <s>aYcizyati</s>, <s>˚te</s>, <s>aYcitum</s>, to bend, curve, incline, curl;\r\n<div n=\"to\"/>to reverence (with inclined body), to honour;\r\n<div n=\"to\"/>to tend, move, go, wander about;\r\n<div n=\"to\"/>to request, <ls>L.</ls> : <ab>cl.</ab> 10. or <ab>Caus.</ab> <s>aYcayati</s>, to unfold, make clear, produce. <ab>Desid.</ab> <ab>P.</ab> <ab>Ā.</ab> <s>aYcicizati</s>, <s>˚te</s>, to be desirous of bending:\r\n<div n=\"vp\"/><ab>Pass.</ab> <s>aYcyate</s> or <s>acyate</s>, to be bent.<info whitneyroots=\"ac,1\"/><info verb=\"genuineroot\" cp=\"1P,1Ā,10P,10Ā\"/>\r\n<LEND>"
    },
